---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Passive Yield Lab — how we handle your data.">
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We use Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand how visitors use our site.
      Cloudflare Analytics is privacy-first: it does not use cookies, does not
      track individual users across sites, and does not collect personal
      information. All data is aggregated and anonymous.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Passive Yield Lab does not set any first-party cookies. We do not use tracking pixels,
      fingerprinting, or any other client-side tracking technology.
    </p>

    <h2>Email Collection</h2>
    <p>
      If you subscribe to our newsletter, your email address is collected and
      managed through <a href="https://www.beehiiv.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Beehiiv</a>,
      a third-party email platform. By subscribing, you agree to Beehiiv's
      privacy policy. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any email.
    </p>
    <p>
      We will never sell, rent, or share your email address with third parties
      for marketing purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p>
      When you click an affiliate link, you will be redirected to a third-party
      website. That website may set its own cookies and collect data according
      to its own privacy policy. We have no control over third-party data
      practices.
    </p>

    <h2>Hosting</h2>
    <p>
      This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect standard
      server log data (IP address, browser type, pages visited) as part of its
      normal operations. Please refer to
      <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>
      for more information.
    </p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Passive Yield Lab is not directed at anyone under the age of 18. We do not knowingly
      collect information from minors.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this
      page with an updated date.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy? Email us at
      <a href="mailto:hello@passiveyieldlab.com">hello@passiveyieldlab.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
